  <num>1-1327</num>
  <heading>Surveyor to certify and record location of party wall.</heading>
  <text>The Surveyor or a registered surveyor shall ascertain and certify, and the Surveyor may put on record, at the request and expense of any person interested therein, the fact of the occupation of land by a party wall, as mentioned in <cite path="§1-1326">§ 1-1326</cite>.</text>
